data.description: Ready to move in! Possession at closing.  HOA All BRICK ~ LARGE HOME AT 1793 square feet ~3 bedrooms/2 full baths ~ lots of living space: family, living, dining & all season rooms. LOTS OF UPDATES: New waterproof hardwood laminate flooring in living, dining, kitchen, family, hallway and bathrooms. New bay window, patio door, kitchen sink and faucet, master bath shower, commode, faucet, lighting and fresh paint. Resurfaced driveway and wood burning fireplace. Fresh paint in master  bedroom. Newer SS stove and microwave, roof with soffits, and gutter including easy to use down spouts. Newer windows throughout home. HVAC has dehumidifier and HEPA filter. Larger Fenced in back yard, W/mini barn & playhouse/shed & paver patio for outdoor enjoyment. Close to everything including highway access to northside and downtown Indy ~ Top rated Brownsburg School System.
